            <title><![CDATA[【#50岁后99.5%的人体内有水痘带状疱疹病毒#[话筒]】带状疱疹俗称“缠腰龙”，#带状疱疹疼痛可能持续数月甚至数年#。研究显示，约99.5%的50岁及以上成人体内都潜...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%2350%E5%B2%81%E5%90%8E99.5%25%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%B4%E7%97%98%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%2350%E5%B2%81%E5%90%8E99.5%25%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%B4%E7%97%98%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#50岁后99.5%的人体内有水痘带状疱疹病毒#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】带状疱疹俗称“缠腰龙”，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%95%B0%E6%9C%88%E7%94%9A%E8%87%B3%E6%95%B0%E5%B9%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%95%B0%E6%9C%88%E7%94%9A%E8%87%B3%E6%95%B0%E5%B9%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#带状疱疹疼痛可能持续数月甚至数年#</span></a>。研究显示，约99.5%的50岁及以上成人体内都潜伏着水痘-带状疱疹病毒，当抵抗力下降时，病毒会被重新激活。数据表明，接种疫苗后，人群整体的带状疱疹发生率可降低90%以上，医生建议50岁以上人群积极接种带状疱疹疫苗👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4894708410023986" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hdcum8x5ehj61x412we8102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/yUhLkxL2lx084XKfdYcU01041200rFhp0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1682648351&amp;ssig=MasnjyvsuY&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.w