            <description><![CDATA[【五一倒计时！出行实用健康帖快码起<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[打call]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a1dacall-1e0c4593fc.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】①<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%87%E5%8B%BF%E6%9A%B4%E9%A5%AE%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%87%E5%8B%BF%E6%9A%B4%E9%A5%AE%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#五一假期切勿暴饮暴食#</span></a>，避免吃隔夜食物或过油过辣食物，以免引发肠胃不适；②扭伤拉伤后切忌马上按摩，24小时内应先冰敷，若长时间肿胀、活动受限，需尽快就医；③被不认识的昆虫叮咬后，若出现疼痛红肿、过敏或发热，务必及时就医；④出游途中注意防晒防暑，晒伤后尽快用毛巾冷敷，避免挑破水泡👇🏻（科普中国）<img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hddzbz5a82j20u01hcq97.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hddzbyft5dj20u01oo7d3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hddzbzyzadj20u01mu119.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hddzc0xbtyj20u01segum.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hddzc2y7ukj20u021iwp8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hddzc6ooj8j20u01o4jzo.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
